U.S. Drone Strike Kills 14 in Pakistan’s Tribal Area, GEO Says

-- B y   H a r i s   A n w a r
-- 
2011-06-06T04:25:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/u-s-drone-strike-kills-14-in-pakistan-s-tribal-area-geo-says.html
A missile strike by an unmanned U.S.
spy plane killed 14 people in  Pakistan ’s tribal area of South
Waziristan, Geo television reported, without saying where it got
the information.  A similar strike on June 3 killed Ilyas Kashmiri, a top al-
Qaeda commander, according to his Harkat-ul Jihad Islami
militant organization and a Pakistani security official.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Haris Anwar in Islamabad at 
 Hanwar2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Hirschberg in Hong Kong at 
 phirschberg@bloomberg.net  